1. e4 c5 2. Nc3 Nc6 3. f4 d6 4. Nf3 g6 5. Bc4 Bg7 6. O-O Nf6 7. d3 O-O 8. Qe1 Nd4 { Rare. We have a fun response. } 9. f5 Nxc2 10. Qh4 Nxa1 11. fxg6 hxg6 { 90% played, but losing move! } 12. Ng5 Nh5 { Their only try... leaving a square attacked three times. } 13. Nxf7 Rxf7 14. Bxf7+ Kh7 15. Qg5 { This is apparently #9. } *


